ServletSecurityFilter - Class in com.epam.training.filter
Class ServletSecurityFilter is a Filter that prohibits access to some of the commands via controller servlet (with parameters inserted into GET request) for Guests and Users (Admins have no limitations) and redirects such requests to the index page.
